    "changelog-item1": "<strong>V20260626 (Global Version)</strong>:<br>1. Integrated Whisper multilingual engine and SenseVoice-Small fast engine, supporting recognition of nearly 100 languages (French, German, Spanish, Italian, etc.).<br>2. Integrated local Ollama offline translation framework, supporting Qwen2.5 3B/7B translation and dropdown selection in extension popup.<br>3. Upgraded UI color scheme to Twilight Indigo theme; restructured installation to 4 steps (with Ollama setup as Step 1).",
    "changelog-item2": "<strong>V20260621 (Initial Release)</strong>:<br>1. Supported SenseVoice fast voice recognition (ZH, EN, JA, KO, Cantonese) and DeepSeek cloud API translation.<br>2. Provided bilingual mode, multi-line historical subtitle scrolling, and translucent glassmorphism overlay." 
